{"tid":925924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】蔣麗芸批美國忘恩負義　稱金融海嘯中國出手相救","createTime":"2018-12-03T05:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T01:52:50.000Z","uid":48973,"like":12,"dislike":228,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cb97a338e3d81268d6d0f87cea5fc1bd31309e","tid":925924,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00001/1543806287596/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E8%94%A3%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%B8%E6%89%B9%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%BF%98%E6%81%A9%E8%B2%A0%E7%BE%A9-%E7%A8%B1%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%B5%B7%E5%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9B%B8%E6%95%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00001%2F1543806287596%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2594%25A3%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%258A%25B8%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BF%2598%25E6%2581%25A9%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2595%2591&d=skePNZIMzG5atM%2FMZUr7wpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9d16cf3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00001%2F1543806287596%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2594%25A3%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%258A%25B8%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BF%2598%25E6%2581%25A9%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2595%2591&h=07551b43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00001/1543806287596/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E8%94%A3%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%B8%E6%89%B9%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%BF%98%E6%81%A9%E8%B2%A0%E7%BE%A9-%E7%A8%B1%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%B5%B7%E5%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9B%B8%E6%95%91</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181203/s00001/743e1cdaae32488af170fb1806a74386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181203%2Fs00001%2F743e1cdaae32488af170fb1806a74386.jpg&h=04de143c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易戰引起國際關注。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸昨（2日）晨在社交網站發帖，批評美國忘恩負義。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸在帖文中，分享上海復旦大學中國研究院長張維為教授的分析短片，留言：「2008年美國面對經濟危機，中國出手相救而令美國得以紓緩，但當美國經濟略有復蘇即忘恩負義。今天美國經濟如履薄冰，危機隨時再現，到時我們還能幫嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n據蔣麗芸上載的短片所見，張維為教授指2008年金融海嘯是由中國社會主義模式，拯救了美國的資本主義模式；又認為人類命運共同體基礎，只能是合作共贏，而非美國奉行的零和博弈。他又稱，中國有一個代表整體人民利益的政黨，「美國今天是找不到的」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，貿易戰方面，中美領導人已達成重要共識，美方同意明年1月1日起暫緩加徵新關稅，中國同意從美國購買「非常大量」的農業等產品；雙方立即就知識產權保護等結構變革談判，爭取在90日內完成，否則美方將繼續對2000億美元中國商品增加關稅。"},{"pid":"e00e096cff4d9f87361d6feec165cb417c082b2c","tid":925924,"uid":10064,"like":228,"dislike":1,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"佢想攞口交部華春蠅個位？"},{"pid":"8e4e4d257e9e0413c11cb31179d081edd7790564","tid":925924,"uid":121146,"like":126,"dislike":1,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"一於主動取消美國關係法啦屌"},{"pid":"0209f3aade3203adf55b47df9e4bd1fbe203e994","tid":925924,"uid":7369,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"咁不如再講下美國畀大陸入世貿啦"},{"pid":"da1437854e7f46f7606dd549f837c4fde956be93","tid":925924,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e731f16a7826c6e3a8e2a44668f7828d56328e7c","tid":925924,"uid":77196,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"佢係咪生活係第二個世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245e500